props.text: You must select a Part ID or Label to run report

config.script:
startDate = self.parent.parent.parent.getChild("Header/Date/StartDate").props.value
	endDate = self.parent.parent.parent.getChild("Header/Date/EndDate").props.value
	partID = self.getSibling("PartIDEntry").props.text
	label = self.getSibling("LabelEntry").props.text
	
	if partID is "":
		partID = None
		
	if label is "":
		label = None
	
	if partID != "" or label != "":
		self.view.params.startTime = startDate
		self.view.params.endTime = endDate
		self.view.params.partId = partID
		self.view.params.label = label
